featured_reviews.review_id: Apsara Mataji is on the left corner in the premises, few 15 steps down. Further down 20 steps there is Heritage Well(vaav) which is almost closed. One can see from only tiny hole. There is Kameshwar Mahadev temple in same premises. Before some time Mahant Kashidatt swaroopji Guru shri Damodar swaroopji stayed here long time and worshiped in this abandon place where so many snakes were there. Currently Mahant Yogi ji is taking care of this premises.
